<div id="review_1408497335" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1408497335" />
    <a title="Kathleen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12425417-kathleen"><img alt="Kathleen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1365087116p2/12425417.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1408497335?book_show_action=true">Oct 04, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathleen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathleen" href="/user/show/12425417-kathleen">Kathleen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/23199508-dead-man-s-ransom">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1408497335" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7041780943189567237">I had forgotten how much I enjoyed Brother Cadfael! Started back on this fine series with it&apos;s excellent dialogue and accurate period detail.<br/><br/>The Welsh were over the borders as King Stephen and Matilda the Empress were fighting their battles. Ellis Peters described the Welsh protagonists and who had or perhaps, may have had allegiances.<br/><br/>I recommend this for every one and especially people like myself wishing to understand some distant Welsh roots.</span>
  <span id="freeText7041780943189567237" style="display:none">I had forgotten how much I enjoyed Brother Cadfael! Started back on this fine series with it's excellent dialogue and accurate period detail.<br /><br />The Welsh were over the borders as King Stephen and Matilda the Empress were fighting their battles. Ellis Peters described the Welsh protagonists and who had or perhaps, may have had allegiances.<br /><br />I recommend this for every one and especially people like myself wishing to understand some distant Welsh roots.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7041780943189567237" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
